All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Chat
Represents a chat entity that encapsulates various properties and actions related to a chat conversation.
ChatConstants
This class contains constant error messages related to chat validation scenarios.
ChatDAO
This class provides data access methods to interact with the chat-related database tables.
ChatService
This class provides services related to chat management, such as register, login, list, update, and delete.
ChatValidator
This class provides methods to validate chat-related data and operations.
ConnectionUtils
This utility class provides methods for establishing a database connection.
DAOException
The `DAOException` class is an exception that can be thrown by data access object (DAO) operations.
InvalidUserException
The `InvalidUserException` class is an exception that can be thrown when user data fails validation.
Invite
Represents an invitation entity that contains information about an invitation event, including its type, date, time, participants, and associated actions.
InviteConstants
This class contains constant error messages related to invite validation scenarios.
InviteDAO
This class provides data access methods to interact with the invite database table.
InviteService
This class provides services related to invite management, such as take, list, update, favourite, and delete.
InviteValidator
This class provides methods to validate invite-related data and operations.
ServiceException
The `ServiceException` class is an exception that can be thrown by service layer operations.
Still
The `Still` class represents a photographic still captured by a user within the FreshNest application.
StillConstants
This class contains constant messages related to still (possibly an image or media content) validation, creation, update, deletion, and other still-related operations.
StillDAO
This class provides data access methods to interact with the stills database table.
StillService
This class provides services related to still management, such as take, list, update, favourite, and delete.
StillValidator
This class provides methods to validate still-related data and operations.
User
The `User` class represents a user within the FreshNest application.
UserConstants
This class contains constant messages related to user validation, registration, login, profile updates, and other user-related operations.
UserDAO
This class provides data access methods to interact with the user database table.
UserService
This class provides services related to user management, such as register, login, list, update, and delete.
UserValidator
This class provides methods to validate user-related data and operations.
